00:27:01,320 --> 00:27:08,420
 I na kraju vidimo kako ne možemo reći crkvi ne,

621
00:27:08,420 --> 00:27:09,660
 a Isusu da.

622
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:12,940
 Zato što je Isus ustanovio crkvu.

623
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:14,460
 On ju je htio takvu.

624
00:27:14,460 --> 00:27:16,100
 Isus je htio crkvu.

625
00:27:16,100 --> 00:27:16,920
 Mi smo grešni.

626
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:20,120
 Ali je Isus htio crkvu koja je sveta.

627
00:27:20,120 --> 00:27:22,260
 Pozvao je 12 apostola.

628
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:24,640
 Je li Isus mogao odabrati ljude

629
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:25,540
 koji su savršeni,

630
00:27:25,540 --> 00:27:26,940
 koji će biti uz njega

631
00:27:26,940 --> 00:27:28,640
 i neće ga ni izdati,

632
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:29,640
 ni otići od njega,

633
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:30,340
 ni napustiti.

634
00:27:30,340 --> 00:27:32,200
 Apsolutno je mogao.

635
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:34,360
 Ali Isus zbira učenike.

636
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:36,860
 Plan, svi su bili kukavice na kraju.

637
00:27:36,860 --> 00:27:38,000
 Jedan ostao.

638
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,880
 Ovaj ga zatajio.

639
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:42,040
 Ali Isus im je oprostio.

640
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,500
 Isto je tako s nama.

641
00:27:44,500 --> 00:27:46,740
 Pas ćemo tisuću puta.

642
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:48,580
 Ali ne mojemo misliti

643
00:27:48,580 --> 00:27:50,220
 da smo daleko od Boga,

644
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:51,220
 da nas Bog ne voli.

645
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:53,740
 To je ono što djavao želi da mislite.

646
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:56,660
 Isus nas poziva u zajednicu.

647
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:58,640
 Isus nam želi oprostiti više

648
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:01,000
 nego što ti sam sebi želiš oprostiti.

649
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:03,380
 I toliko je možda stvari i grijeha

650
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:05,440
 koje non stop nam se vraćaju na pamet.

651
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,380
 Pusti to.

652
00:28:06,380 --> 00:28:08,060
 Ono što je ispovjeđeno,

653
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:10,280
 to pusti Bogu.

654
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:12,140
 Živi danas.

655
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:13,820
 Opet ponavljam,

656
00:28:13,820 --> 00:28:16,240
 nemoj kopati po prošlosti.

657
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:18,600
 Prekrasno mi je bilo

658
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:23,920
 kad je Isus govorio Savlu u viđenju

659
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:28,540
 Savle, Savle, zašto me progoniš?

660
00:28:28,540 --> 00:28:31,800
 Nije govorio zašto progoniš moje kršćane,

661
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:34,920
 nego je govorio zašto me progoniš.

662
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,680
 O čemu se to uradi?

663
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:41,660
 Mi smo progonili Isusa u tim kršćanima.

664
00:28:42,540 --> 00:28:44,020
 Kasnije Isus kaže,

665
00:28:44,020 --> 00:28:47,380
 što god učiniste jednome od moje najmanje braće,

666
00:28:47,380 --> 00:28:48,700
 meni učiniste.

667
00:28:48,700 --> 00:28:50,900
 Doslovno Isusu učiniste.

668
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:52,020
 Kaže,

669
00:28:52,020 --> 00:28:53,980
 bijah goli za odijenu ste me,

670
00:28:53,980 --> 00:28:57,820
 bijah u tamnici i posjetili ste me.

671
00:28:57,820 --> 00:28:59,980
 Sve što ste učinili,

672
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:02,140
 jednom od najmlađe moje braće,

673
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:03,700
 meni ste učinili.

674
00:29:04,540 --> 00:29:09,340
 I tu Isus doslovno govori da je dio crkve,

675
00:29:09,340 --> 00:29:10,420
 da je crkva.

676
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:13,780
 I nije biblijski reći crkvi da,

677
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:15,920
 Kristu da,

678
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,900
 a crkvi ne.

679
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:19,400
 jer je to isprepleteno.

680
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,800
 Što nam je činiti?

681
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:24,940
 Kod nas je velik problem nerazumijevanja.

682
00:29:24,940 --> 00:29:27,220
 Ako nešto ne upoznaš,

683
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:30,800
 ne možeš ne vidjeti da je nešto važno.

684
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:32,300
 Ja se sjećam,

685
00:29:32,300 --> 00:29:33,340
 kod nas u samostanu,

686
00:29:33,340 --> 00:29:34,420
 ovo sam spominjao,

687
00:29:34,420 --> 00:29:38,140
 bio je jedan časni brat.

688
00:29:38,140 --> 00:29:40,120
 To vam je kod časna sestra samo muško.

689
00:29:40,120 --> 00:29:41,260
 Logično.

690
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:44,340
 Ovo je najbolje objašnjenje ikad.

691
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:45,280
 Časni brat.

692
00:29:45,280 --> 00:29:47,800
 I on je čuo kako je jedan naš fratar

693
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:49,540
 otišao u studiji na Rim,

694
00:29:49,540 --> 00:29:51,320
 u Rim, na studiji.

695
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:53,240
 I pita,

696
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:55,280
 pa što je on otišao?

697
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:57,420
 Kaže, otišao u Rim.

698
00:29:57,420 --> 00:29:58,840
 Pa što će raditi tamo?

699
00:29:58,840 --> 00:29:59,640
 Pa studirat će.

700
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:01,460
 Kaže, pa što će studirat?

701
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:02,640
 Liturgiku.

702
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:05,540
 Kaže, pa šta to ima studirat?

703
00:30:05,540 --> 00:30:07,140
 Upališ sviće,

704
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,440
 kažeš misu,

705
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,840
 ugasiš sviće.

706
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:12,640
 Njemu je to bilo dovoljno.

707
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:15,380
 On je sve tu misu vidio

708
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:16,980
 na tako jednostavan način

709
00:30:16,980 --> 00:30:18,800
 da upališ sviće,

710
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:20,220
 slaviš misu,

711
00:30:20,220 --> 00:30:21,040
 ugasiš sviće.

712
00:30:21,040 --> 00:30:22,400
 Šta to ima študirat?

713
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,600
 I druga stvar

714
00:30:24,600 --> 00:30:26,720
 koju ja stalno prepričavam,

715
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,880
 ja sam ovako smotan u čeljade dosta.

716
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,580
 Mi na humcu,

717
00:30:30,580 --> 00:30:33,180
 na humcu uz muzej,

718
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:34,580
 smo imali lapidari

719
00:30:34,580 --> 00:30:37,980
 i u tom lapidariji su oni veliki ostaci,

720
00:30:37,980 --> 00:30:40,000
 nadgrobni spomenici.

721
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:43,260
 Ja sam otišao to malo počistiti.

722
00:30:43,260 --> 00:30:45,440
 Vidim dolje neke kamenčiće,

723
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:47,120
 tu hrpica ovdje,

724
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:47,640
 hrpica,

725
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,660
 bože moj,

726
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:49,960
 opet su nešto razbacali

727
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:51,140
 i ništa.

728
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:52,000
 Ja uzmem metlu,

729
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:52,920
 uzmem kantu,

730
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:53,980
 pometem,

731
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:55,240
 to je te sve kamenčiće

732
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:56,700
 i sve stavim u jednu kantu,

733
00:30:56,700 --> 00:30:56,920
 reku,

734
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,940
 ako im bude trebalo,

735
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:58,640
 tu je.

736
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:01,420
 I dolazi ovaj arheolog,

737
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:03,040
 kad je on to vidio.

738
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:05,820
 čovjeku se tlakovi sastali.

739
00:31:07,820 --> 00:31:10,160
 Svaka ta hrpica je bilo stoljeće.

740
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:14,600
 Ja sam njemu to počistio.

741
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:19,960
 Meni je to bila nakupina kamenčića

742
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:20,840
 koji tu stoje,

743
00:31:20,840 --> 00:31:22,300
 ja ne mogu proći smetaju mi,

744
00:31:22,300 --> 00:31:24,300
 a njemu su to bila stoljeća.

745
00:31:24,300 --> 00:31:26,800
 Ja sam njemu nekih 500, 600 godina

746
00:31:26,800 --> 00:31:28,480
 smeo u jednu kantu

747
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,920
 da mu je to na jednom mjestu.

748
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,580
 Čovjeku nije dobro bilo.

749
00:31:31,580 --> 00:31:32,940
 Zašto?

750
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:35,980
 Zato što ja te stvari ne kužim.

751
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:37,500
 Meni je to kamen,

752
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:39,040
 njemu je to vrijedni nalaz.

753
00:31:39,040 --> 00:31:40,800
 Kako se to kaže?

754
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:42,920
 Vrijedni nešto.

755
00:31:42,920 --> 00:31:43,720
 Kamen.

756
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:47,480
 Ali upravo zato što ja

757
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:49,560
 ne razumijem,

758
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:50,840
 ne znam o tome dovoljno,

759
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,680
 ne mogu to ni znati cijeniti.

760
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:55,020
 Isto je tako o svetoj misi

761
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,000
 i o crkvi.

762
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:58,460
 Ako ne upoznajemo svetu misu,

763
00:31:58,460 --> 00:32:00,580
 ako ne upoznajemo svoju crku,

764
00:32:00,580 --> 00:32:02,700
 nećemo je moći dovoljno

765
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:04,600
 ni voljeti, ni cijeniti.

766
00:32:04,600 --> 00:32:07,120
 i samo ćemo se lijepiti

767
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:09,260
 na ove vijesti,

768
00:32:09,260 --> 00:32:11,780
 na ovu žutu štampu

769
00:32:11,780 --> 00:32:13,460
 i na sve ono što nam iskoči.

770
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:15,560
 Vi znate da

771
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:17,420
 nijedna dobra stvar nije vijest.

772
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:19,200
 Rijedko kad ćete čuti

773
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,640
 da je nešto pozitivno.

774
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,120
 Antunovski hod.

775
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:24,940
 Više ćeš stvari vidjeti

776
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:27,160
 o negativnim situacijama

777
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,460
 nego nešto što je prekrasno

778
00:32:28,460 --> 00:32:29,180
 kao vaš hod

779
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:30,600
 i ostale stvari koje radite.

780
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:33,240
 I tako isto s nama svećenicima.

781
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:36,160
 Vi znate da tisuće aviona lete,

782
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:38,620
 ali nije da nije vijest

783
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:40,980
 nego onaj koji se srušio.

784
00:32:42,120 --> 00:32:43,660
 Kad raste cijela šuma,

785
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:45,260
 to se ništa ne čuje.

786
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:46,820
 Cijela šuma izrasla

787
00:32:46,820 --> 00:32:47,940
 bez ikakvog zvuka.

788
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:49,860
 Ali kad jedno drvo padne,

789
00:32:49,860 --> 00:32:51,340
 to si tekako čuje.

790
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:54,460
 Ima prekrasnih svetih svećenika.

791
00:32:54,460 --> 00:32:56,640
 Ima svetih ljudi...

792
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:59,480
 Rekao sam svetih.

793
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,980
 Šalim se.

794
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:04,360
 Ima svetih ljudi koji žive,

795
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:06,020
 koji su predani Bogu.

796
00:33:06,020 --> 00:33:08,240
 I nemojte dopustiti

797
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:10,520
 da vam jedna mrlja

798
00:33:10,520 --> 00:33:13,300
 zamagli cijeli pogled.

799
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:14,800
 Ja se sjećam,

800
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:16,980
 jedan je svećenik molio

801
00:33:16,980 --> 00:33:19,400
 kako želi postati proziran.

802
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:22,180
 Niči veze što se postati proziran.

803
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:22,780
 Glupo.

804
00:33:22,780 --> 00:33:25,000
 I kad malo bolje razmislim,

805
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:27,180
 možda nešto najveće,

806
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,880
 što jedan svećenik može napraviti

807
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:30,820
 je postati proziran.

808
00:33:30,820 --> 00:33:33,220
 Da ljudi više ne vide tebe,

809
00:33:33,220 --> 00:33:35,380
 nego da vide Krista.

810
00:33:35,380 --> 00:33:37,700
 I možemo se pitati,

811
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:40,080
 jesam li ja nekome prepreka do Boga?

812
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:42,600
 Jesam li ja nekome poticaj

813
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:44,940
 ili spoticaj do Boga?

814
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,320
 Jao meni,

815
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:48,400
 ako neko zbog mene napusti crkvu,

816
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,960
 ali blago meni,

817
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,800
 ako neko zbog mene uzljubi

818
00:33:51,800 --> 00:33:52,940
 više Krista.

819
00:33:52,940 --> 00:33:55,160
 I isto je tako pitanje

820
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,180
 za sve nas ovdje.

821
00:33:57,120 --> 00:33:58,680
 Ako je svatko od nas crkva,

822
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:02,460
 kakav ja primjer dajem

823
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:04,200
 kao crkva?

824
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:05,900
 Je li ljudi zbog mene

825
00:34:05,900 --> 00:34:08,220
 požele upoznati moga Boga

826
00:34:08,220 --> 00:34:09,860
 ili ljudi zbog mene

827
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:12,060
 požele otići

828
00:34:12,060 --> 00:34:13,140
 iz crkve?

829
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,480
 na kraju

830
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:18,720
 Prastjepan vam je govorio

831
00:34:18,720 --> 00:34:20,140
 o ispovjedi,

832
00:34:20,140 --> 00:34:21,580
 o molitvi.

833
00:34:21,580 --> 00:34:23,900
 Ima jedan stari tekst

834
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:26,040
 koji je govorio o pobožnosti

835
00:34:26,040 --> 00:34:27,820
 i o duhovnosti.

836
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:30,960
 I stavio bih vam uistinu na srce

837
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:32,680
 da budete i pobožni

838
00:34:32,680 --> 00:34:33,780
 i duhovni.

839
00:34:34,220 --> 00:34:35,560
 nije isto biti pobožan

840
00:34:35,560 --> 00:34:36,920
 i biti duhovan.

841
00:34:37,780 --> 00:34:39,580
 Pobožnost je sredstvo

842
00:34:39,580 --> 00:34:41,440
 a duhovnost je cilj.

843
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:44,520
 pobožnost se može postići

844
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:45,640
 disciplinom.

845
00:34:45,640 --> 00:34:46,580
 Svaki dan,

846
00:34:46,580 --> 00:34:47,560
 trš, trš, trš, trš,

847
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:48,760
 to tako, tako i tako.

848
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:50,300
 Ti ćeš izgledati pobožan.

849
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:52,320
 Ali ako ta pobožnost

850
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:53,540
 ne mijenja tvoju nutrinu,

851
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:55,580
 ti nikad nećeš postati duhovan.

852
00:34:55,580 --> 00:34:57,140
 Samo ćeš ploviti.

853
00:34:57,140 --> 00:34:58,480
 Plutati.

854
00:34:58,480 --> 00:35:00,140
 Ja to volim usporediti

855
00:35:00,140 --> 00:35:01,340
 sa plastičnom bocom.

856
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:03,560
 Ako vi zatvorite plastičnu bocu

857
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:04,820
 i bacite je na more,

858
00:35:04,820 --> 00:35:05,620
 u more,

859
00:35:05,620 --> 00:35:07,340
 ona će cijeli svoj život

860
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:08,060
 samo plutati.

861
00:35:08,060 --> 00:35:09,860
 Ali ako joj otvorite čep,

862
00:35:09,860 --> 00:35:11,300
 ona će potonuti

863
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:12,460
 i pašće lijepo na dno.

864
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:14,120
 Napunit će se vodom.

865
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:15,300
 Isto je tako nam.

866
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:17,080
 Mi možemo dolaziti,

867
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:17,740
 moliti,

868
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:19,720
 ako ostanemo začepljeni,

869
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:20,940
 samo ćemo plutati.

870
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:23,480
 Ali naš cilj nije da plutamo,

871
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:25,520
 nego da stvarno dopustimo Krista

872
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:28,140
 da natopi naša srca.

873
00:35:28,140 --> 00:35:31,820
 I zadnja, moja misao,

874
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:33,560
 to jest nije moja misao,

875
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:34,480
 nego ovo što želim

876
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,640
 podijeliti s vama,

877
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:40,060
 Rastjepan će se isto osjetiti,

878
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:42,640
 kad smo bili na fakultetu,

879
00:35:42,640 --> 00:35:45,600
 mi smo toliko dobrih stvari učili i čuli,

880
00:35:45,600 --> 00:35:50,040
 ali te kasnije to nekako sjedne sve na svoje.

881
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:52,420
 Ima jedna poznata

882
00:35:52,420 --> 00:35:55,780
 od Karla Ranera od crkvi,

883
00:35:55,780 --> 00:35:57,460
 kada kaže,

884
00:35:57,460 --> 00:36:00,620
 crkva je stara žena

885
00:36:00,620 --> 00:36:03,640
 s mnogim ožiljcima i borama,

886
00:36:03,640 --> 00:36:06,100
 ali ona je moja majka,

887
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:08,500
 a majku se ne tuče.

888
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:11,240
 Crkva je moja majka,

889
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:13,140
 a majku se ne tuče.

890
00:36:13,140 --> 00:36:15,480
 Volite svoju crkvu,

891
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,560
 volite svoju majku,

892
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:19,280
 čuvajte je,

893
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,100
 liječite je,

894
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,800
 pomažite joj,

895
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:24,340
 budite dio nje,

896
00:36:24,340 --> 00:36:26,220
 a nemojte je tući.

897
00:36:26,220 --> 00:36:28,500
 Amen.

898
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:30,100
 Valja Nisus i Marija.

899
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:34,440
 I tako si živ

900
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:37,800
 i tako te osjećaj.

901
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:41,480
 Bog vas blagoslovio.

902
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:41,900
 Hvala.

